Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please use this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's settling down in a bad spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The center of the three children's rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To make it easier for her to watch us...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was distracted by the tracking devices\Nthat I didn't think we would get another adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually we should be happy about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carol and Sister Krone.\NWe have two more sources of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First, where did those two come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carol is Conny's replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So they're replenishing the merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if this place is a farm,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,they must have a site where they\Nprepare one-year-olds for replenishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So did all of us come from there originally?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably. And also that Sister Krone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's significant that there's\Nanother adult other than Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There might be other farms just like here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so are the adults who obey the demons\Nunder the control of demons from birth,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or after they're captured?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After we escape,\Nthings will change depending on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But first, we need to figure out\Nhow to escape with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the location of the tracking devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I searched all over my body, but I didn't find\Nany traces of something implanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And nothing in our clothes or shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Based on humankind's existing technology,\Nit probably uses radio waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that requires batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something really small that wouldn't leave a scar,\Nand with batteries that last over 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of product wouldn't exist in 2015.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll be difficult to predict the mechanism,\Nfind the location, and figure out how to break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And we might as well give up\Nif it's technology originating from the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? So, checkmate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even if we can't figure it out,\Nwe can guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We have to think\Nfrom the enemy's point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where and what kind of a device\Nwould be the most convenient to implant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carol!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since she just arrived, she might have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A mark from implanting the tracking device.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for an opportunity\Nto return to this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I only made a request for one assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I called for you specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of your many achievements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The youngest to be selected\Nas Mom and caretaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've raised the highest number of high-quality\Ngoods among all of the plants, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am honored to work under\Nsomeone I admire so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lip service isn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's quit the small talk,\Nand talk about work instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here are the documents\Nof my adorable children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Memorize all of it, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It should be easier\Nthan getting perfect scores every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what work was I called in for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They found out about the secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They also saw the package in the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, in accordance with the rules,\Nwe must find them and ship them imm—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's fine. I already have an idea\Nof who the targets are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Two of the oldest children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We just have to make sure\Nthey don't escape before shipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}My children are special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And this is beneficial for the plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So you're not reporting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No. I will take care of the targets\Nin a proper manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You are a guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You don't need to think.\NJust watch the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I am the Mom of this House.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And you are my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understand? Sister Krone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am, Isabella.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised, too.\NTo think that the amazing Isabella...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And she's not reporting it to the higher-ups,\Nbut trying to cover up her mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, if I help her out here, she'll owe me,\Nand I'll one day have the Mom position!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're crying so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, don't cry.\NYou'd be happy too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I became a Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, I'll get busier,\Nbut you'll support me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get jealous of the other children\Nand say selfish things, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be my chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can become a Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not one day, but now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:07:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I capture the children who know the secret\Nand report her violation, Isabella will be fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would be faster to pretend to obey her\Nand then take her position away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Capture the targets!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then snitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then immediately ship them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become the Mom here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I need to find them quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The kids like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. How do we outmaneuver\Nthe two adults who are liked so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The biggest concern\Nis the report to the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as we escape,\Nthe monsters will come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one way to stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom and Sister will have to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:08:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman and Ray, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you get perfect scores on the tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you. I hope we can get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did she hear us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that sister came here\Njust to watch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The way she looked at us was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably suspecting us,\Nthe oldest among everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she get that information?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious? From Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom is definitely closing in on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Think from the enemy's point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Demons won't eat the tracking device.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That means it'd be in a place\Nwhere it's easily remov—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That night...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What's that? A bug bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mom told me a while ago that this was\Nfrom when blood was drawn to test for diseases.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Naila, Phil, Mark, and Conny all had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}On everyone's ear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mine too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course. I'm 10, and you're 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It was way smaller than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I meant, it was such a small scar\Nthat it had already disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to protect these kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scheduled check-in. Scheduled check-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is 73584, Plant Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,October 17th. Everything is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now ending transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isabella?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a message from the Boss.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Those three can be shipped out\Nas scheduled, right?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen, Isabella.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This year, the other plants\Nhave overall been bearing poor fruit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only your plant can deliver the supreme goods\Nthat will be offered at the Tifari.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've understood that from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please give the Boss this message.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Everything is going fine.\NYou may have any child at any time."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So they can be shipped?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That would certainly please Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess this up. His meal is special,\Nand nothing like ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, my friends, let us celebrate the harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And offer our prayers to Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no one would notice this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew about a mark\Nfrom when they took our blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it's something\Nthat disappears so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:12:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I didn't even suspect it at all\Nthis whole time. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, you did well, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We now know the location, shape, and size\Nof the tracking device.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can move to the next step.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After locating it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How to break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?\NIf we cut it open to inspect it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Mom combs through our hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...she'll know immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, putting aside to see\Nif we can break it easily or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the tracking device implanted in us\Nisn't that functionally useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? They aren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's because the signal\Ncan't specify the individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without confirming, she can't tell where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we get close to the gate or walls,\Nit doesn't notify her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still implanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They must be confident they can come after us\Nas long as the tracking device is intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Does that mean if it does notify them,\Nit'd be when the tracking device is destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a possibility, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:13:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They would be notified only when it's broken,\Nlike with an alarm or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So if we destroy it,\NMom will know immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if a notification function even exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But thinking that Mom purposely let us know\Nabout the existence of the tracking devices...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't dismiss it so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's risky to mess with it and break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we can only destroy it when we escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then how will we figure out how to break it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for that, this shape and size\Nbrings something to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you leave this issue to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're saying so, then I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing left\Nis taking everyone outside with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is that everyone\Ncompletely trusts Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and they probably won't be able\Nto handle the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we'll have to lie to them\Nto take them outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's also the problem of insufficient abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In simpler terms, they're a hindrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Some aren't good at physical activities,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we have babies who can hardly walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For that, I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Playing tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman is "It," and everyone runs away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We pretend it's play\Nwhen we're actually training.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That way, Mom won't find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach them how to utilize their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- As for how to utilize their brains...\N- Leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Think. What can you do to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman won't overlook things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Check the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which way makes it is easier to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. Downwind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is cool.\NI can last a lot longer than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can even make it—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was doing so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just leave your own footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have to check\Nthe opponent's footprints, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And Norman is also reading your habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For example, Thoma, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Playing tag looks like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get along with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's play tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The match's time limit will be 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be "It."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, try to run away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seven, eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nine, ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let me see what that woman's\Nspecial children can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, how will the enemy move?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She'll probably look for us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And on the way,\Nshe'll capture as many little ones as she can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fake ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what is with this silence?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's not coming after us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:16:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did she change her strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, caught you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did everyone gather in one spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She used these to lure in the younger ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So she's not stupid, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen everyone! Sister is really hard to beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don and Gilda, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was crazy. She chased me everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We got caught way faster\Nthan when Norman was "It."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cover your mouths!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Running while carrying two kids.\NYou must be tired, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to move unless you rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?\NNorman's weakness is physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he was feeble when he was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray's weakness is that\Nhe's a little quick to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He makes a decision fast\Nbut abandons them just as quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your weakness is your naiveté.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like how naive you are by carrying others\Nwhen you're being chased.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up and come on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do you wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:19:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Emma.\NIf you saw the harvest that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How much time is left?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eight minutes and 40 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So these are the perfect scorers of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- They did it!\N- Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman. Ray. Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That sister hasn't done anything since.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably Mom's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom used to suspect us,\Nbut it doesn't seem like that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Norman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom did something behind the scenes\Nso she won't have to move herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think would be\Nthe easiest situation for Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That would be to know our moves\Nwithout having to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there are no security cameras\Nor listening devices...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...already a different person watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely among the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm hungry!\N- Me too.
